Text: I don't know you very well... but okay.

Anything you wish, so long as I can keep growing stronger.
Oh, yes! My training is truly paying off.

Okay. I could use a few minutes to feel the sun shine on my skin.

Follow you? Why would I? (Hmm maybe I'll be leaded to some Corsola) Actually, I will, let's go stranger!

Alright!

Thank you for waiting. |We've restored your Pokémon to full health.
We hope to see you again!
Your pokeballs are empty...|Return with them and try again. |Sorry!

Absolutely. I've never enjoyed anything more.
Come back when you can. This is too good to stop.
